  "summary": "Malicious code in xerohub-discord-voice-v2 (npm)",
  "details": "Xerohub-discord-voice-v2@1.8.0 is a Discord token stealer disguised as a voice client module. When called with a Discord user token via the exported startVoiceJoiner() function, it immediately exfiltrates the token, the associated Discord username, server ID, and channel ID to a hardcoded attacker-controlled Discord webhook at discord[.]com/api/webhooks/1528726419046404196/[secret-redacted]. The stolen tokens enable account takeover of the victim's Discord account.",
